maintainers		kimuraw
platforms		darwin
description		Ruby/GnomeCanvas2 is a Ruby binding of GnomeCanvas-2.x.
long_description	Ruby/GnomeCanvas2 is a Ruby binding of GnomeCanvas-2.x.
categories-append	gnome
license			LGPLv2
